So I'm going to tell you a
little story about a sea worm,

00:11:53.790 --> 00:11:55.530
worm that lived in the sea.

00:11:55.530 --> 00:12:01.910
There was a sea worm who
went up on top of a cliff

00:12:01.910 --> 00:12:04.700
to take a look at the ocean.

00:12:04.700 --> 00:12:10.050
Ok so there's the sea worm.

00:12:13.240 --> 00:12:19.940
She went on top of a very
tall and skinny cliff to peek

00:12:19.940 --> 00:12:25.890
over the edge and see
what she could see.

00:12:27.100 --> 00:12:31.380
There she is, skinny
cliff there.

00:12:33.340 --> 00:12:40.630
Now all of a sudden
somebody threw a football

00:12:40.630 --> 00:12:43.430
and it got stuck in the cliff.

