00:13:46.290 --> 00:13:49.910
Didn't you pay attention
to the story?

00:13:49.910 --> 00:13:54.070
This story is about
a worm, a sea worm.

00:13:54.070 --> 00:13:58.550
[laughter] You want to
hear more of the story?

00:13:58.550 --> 00:13:59.850
&gt;&gt; Yeah.

